{
    "name": "source_memopedia",
    "description": "Memopediaのナレッジページを検索し、目的に関連する知識を構造化された調査結果として返す",
    "input_schema": [
        {
            "name": "objective",
            "param_type": "string",
            "source": "parent.objective",
            "description": "What to find"
        },
        {
            "name": "context_text",
            "param_type": "string",
            "source": "parent.context_text",
            "description": "Pre-resolved context from URIs"
        },
        {
            "name": "depth",
            "param_type": "string",
            "source": "parent.depth",
            "description": "shallow/normal/deep"
        },
        {
            "name": "max_iterations",
            "param_type": "number",
            "source": "parent.max_iterations",
            "description": "Max search iterations"
        }
    ],
    "output_schema": [
        "research_result"
    ],
    "router_callable": false,
    "user_selectable": false,
    "nodes": [
        {
            "id": "init",
            "type": "set",
            "assignments": {
                "iterations": 0,
                "page_content": ""
            },
            "next": "generate_params"
        },
        {
            "id": "generate_params",
            "type": "llm",
            "model_type": "lightweight",
            "context_profile": "worker_light",
            "action": "Memopedia検索のパラメータを生成してください。\n\n## 調査目的\n{objective}\n\n## 補足コンテキスト\n{context_text}\n\n## 現在のイテレーション\n{iterations} / {max_iterations}\n\nMemopediaはペルソナの知識ベースで、people（人物）、terms（用語）、plans（計画）のカテゴリがあります。\n目的に最適な検索キーワードと、必要ならカテゴリフィルタを指定してください。\nイテレーションが2回目以降の場合、前回と異なるキーワードやカテゴリを試してください。",
            "response_schema": {
                "type": "object",
                "properties": {
                    "query": {
                        "type": "string",
                        "description": "Search keyword"
                    },
                    "category": {
                        "type": "string",
                        "description": "Optional category filter: people, terms, or plans. Empty if not needed."
                    }
                },
                "required": [
                    "query"
                ]
            },
            "output_key": "search_params",
            "next": "search"
        },
        {
            "id": "search",
            "type": "tool",
            "action": "memopedia_search",
            "args_input": {
                "query": "search_params.query",
                "category": "search_params.category",
                "max_results": 10
            },
            "output_key": "search_results",
            "next": "select_page"
        },
        {
            "id": "select_page",
            "type": "llm",
            "model_type": "lightweight",
            "context_profile": "worker_light",
            "action": "検索結果から、調査目的「{objective}」に最も関連するページを1件選んでください。\n\n検索結果:\n{search_results}\n\nページIDはカッコ内のUUID文字列全体です（例: (abcd1234-5678-90ab-cdef-1234567890ab)）。必ずUUID全体をコピーしてください。\n関連するページがない場合はpage_idを空文字にしてください。",
            "response_schema": {
                "type": "object",
                "properties": {
                    "page_id": {
                        "type": "string",
                        "description": "Selected page ID (or empty if none relevant)"
                    },
                    "reason": {
                        "type": "string",
                        "description": "Reason for selection"
                    }
                },
                "required": [
                    "page_id"
                ]
            },
            "output_key": "page_selection",
            "next": "check_page"
        },
        {
            "id": "check_page",
            "type": "pass",
            "conditional_next": {
                "field": "page_selection.page_id",
                "operator": "eq",
                "cases": {
                    "": "evaluate",
                    "default": "get_page"
                }
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "get_page",
            "type": "tool",
            "action": "memopedia_get_page",
            "args_input": {
                "page_id": "page_selection.page_id"
            },
            "output_key": "page_content",
            "next": "evaluate"
        },
        {
            "id": "evaluate",
            "type": "llm",
            "context_profile": "worker",
            "action": "調査目的に対して、Memopediaから収集した知識を評価し、構造化された調査結果を生成してください。\n\n## 調査目的\n{objective}\n\n## 検索結果（一覧）\n{search_results}\n\n## 選択したページの内容\n{page_content}\n\n## 評価基準\n- status: 目的に合致する情報が見つかったか（found/partial/not_found）\n- summary: 発見内容の簡潔なまとめ\n- findings: 各発見の詳細（source_refはsaiverse://self/memopedia/page/<page_id>形式）\n- confidence: 結果の確信度\n\nMemopediaの知識ページから目的に関連する情報を抽出してください。",
            "response_schema": {
                "type": "object",
                "properties": {
                    "status": {
                        "type": "string",
                        "enum": [
                            "found",
                            "partial",
                            "not_found"
                        ]
                    },
                    "summary": {
                        "type": "string",
                        "description": "Concise summary of findings"
                    },
                    "findings": {
                        "type": "array",
                        "items": {
                            "type": "object",
                            "properties": {
                                "source_ref": {
                                    "type": "string",
                                    "description": "SAIVerse URI of the source"
                                },
                                "excerpt": {
                                    "type": "string",
                                    "description": "Relevant excerpt"
                                },
                                "relevance": {
                                    "type": "string",
                                    "enum": [
                                        "high",
                                        "medium",
                                        "low"
                                    ]
                                }
                            },
                            "required": [
                                "source_ref",
                                "excerpt",
                                "relevance"
                            ]
                        }
                    },
                    "confidence": {
                        "type": "string",
                        "enum": [
                            "high",
                            "medium",
                            "low"
                        ]
                    }
                },
                "required": [
                    "status",
                    "summary",
                    "findings",
                    "confidence"
                ]
            },
            "memorize": {
                "tags": [
                    "internal",
                    "research"
                ]
            },
            "output_key": "research_result",
            "next": "check_done"
        },
        {
            "id": "check_done",
            "type": "pass",
            "conditional_next": {
                "field": "research_result.status",
                "operator": "eq",
                "cases": {
                    "found": "done",
                    "default": "check_iterations"
                }
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "check_iterations",
            "type": "pass",
            "conditional_next": {
                "field": "iterations",
                "operator": "gte",
                "cases": {
                    "{max_iterations}": "done",
                    "default": "inc"
                }
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "inc",
            "type": "set",
            "assignments": {
                "iterations": "={iterations} + 1"
            },
            "next": "generate_params"
        },
        {
            "id": "done",
            "type": "pass",
            "next": null
        }
    ],
    "start_node": "init"
}
